"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-world-europe-strike-closes-eiffel-tower-in-blow-to-tourists-ahead-of-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get ST's newsletters delivered to your inbox  The strike started on Feb 19 in protest over the way the monument is managed financially.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.925544772874e-13, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703097123, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: REUTERS  PublishedFeb 19, 2024, 08:59 PM  UpdatedFeb 20, 2024, 06:56 PM  PARIS - The Eiffel Tower, one of the world's top tourist attractions, will remain closed for a second straight day on Feb 20 as staff extend a strike, a union representative told AFP.\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 592, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.99999998945691, \"rank\": 5.561748707345608e-09, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The strike started on Feb 19 in protest over the way the monument is managed financially.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The tower's operator, Societe d'Exploitation de la Tour Eiffel (SETE), said on its website that \\\"visits of the monument will be disrupted on Tuesday\\\".\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 737, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Tour_Eiffel_(Hopi_Hari)\", \"score\": 0.9999999995836788, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"la Tour Eiffel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Tour_Eiffel_(Hopi_Hari)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Tour_Eiffel_(Hopi_Hari)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It advised ticket holders to check its website before showing up, or to postpone their visit.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"E-ticket holders were asked to check their e-mails for further information.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The strike comes as Paris prepares to host the 2024 Summer Olympics, which begin on July 26 and will feature metal from the tower in the winners' medals.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1032, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996205133, \"rank\": 3.7947625383029137e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Visitors stood outside the barriers of the tower grounds in front of a giant screen announcing the strike.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a real shame, really, because we come just for three days, and we are not going to be able to get up,\\\" Mr Nelson Navarro, from Norfolk, England, said.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1387, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelson_Navarro\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nelson Navarro\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelson_Navarro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelson_Navarro\"}, {\"begin\": 1408, \"end\": 1415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norfolk\", \"score\": 0.9956634751837381, \"rank\": 0.004355412168626765, \"text\": \"Norfolk\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norfolk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norfolk\"}, {\"begin\": 1417, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\", \"score\": 0.6338602977117074, \"rank\": 0.5292097558730091, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Vito Santos, from Canada, had planned to revisit the monument 15 years after his honeymoon and show if off to his children.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1436, \"end\": 1440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vito_Corleone\", \"score\": 0.8845049614436793, \"rank\": 0.12586657788538863, \"text\": \"Vito\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vito_Corleone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vito_Corleone\"}, {\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999971216337187, \"rank\": 2.712387412591489e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's disappointing...\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The plan was to come here really early to get a ticket as early as possible.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it was a surprise for us, the strike is here, so we cannot make the tour,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unions claim Paris City Hall, which owns 99 per cent of SETE, is underestimating the cost of maintenance and repairs to the monument planned ahead of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This in turn could result in lax maintenance work and put visitors at risk, they say.\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 2005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the second time this year staff have gone on strike for the same reason.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The wrought-iron 324m-high tower, built by Gustave Eiffel in the late 19th century, welcomes about six million visitors each year.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustave_Eiffel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gustave Eiffel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustave_Eiffel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustave_Eiffel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AFP, REUTERS  Tourist attractions  France  Strikes  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 2255, \"end\": 2261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9981391240762733, \"rank\": 0.0015258880072321253, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2304, \"end\": 2312, \"title